Thought this might be useful: If you're exporting to vCards and importing to your address book, and want to retain first/middle/last name so you can merge w/existing contacts, here's a regexp (for Textmate).<p>Find: FN:(\S+) ((\S+( \S+)?) )?(\S+)
Replace: N:(?2:$5;$1;$3;;:$5;$1;;;)\n$0<p>N:Smith;John;J.;;
FN:John J. Smith
